# Should $PSScriptRoot be added to foreach-object-Parallel？

Currently, this automatic variable is not implemented. Use & "${PSScriptRoot}/xxx.ps1 in a child thread, an error will be reported.

## Proposed technical implementation details (optional)
```
 xxx | ForEach-Object  -Parallel {
		${PSScriptRoot} = $using:PSScriptRoot #default add this line
		& "${PSScriptRoot}/xxx.ps1"
}
```
@PaulHigin
